# Trigger building the world model from the current tray camera frame.
# The node runs OBB inference, pairs handles with bodies, computes grasp
# points, projects to world frame, and returns everything as both a
# structured JSON string (for the LLM) and ROS messages (for ROS subscribers).
#
# Request: empty - the configured tray camera namespace is used.
---
bool success
string message
string world_model_json
tracking_pkg/ToolDetectionArray tools_detected
tracking_pkg/GraspCandidateArray grasp_candidates
